header.gameNote: OHIO VALLEY CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - FINAL

videos.description: Ja Morant jars the ball loose on one end of the court, then gets fed by Devin Gilmore for an easy layup on the other end to give Murray State the lead 18-16.
videos.headline: Morant pops ball loose, scores on other end

videos.description: Murray State's KJ Williams jumps up and swats away Kevin McClain's 3-point attempt with authority.
videos.headline: Williams gets ferocious block from behind the arc

videos.description: Shaq Buchanan steals the ball, then flips it to Ja Morant who sinks a 3 to give Murray State a 41-40 lead.
videos.headline: Morant cools himself off after draining go-ahead 3

videos.description: Ja Morant comes away with a mean rejection, then gets the ball back and scores lefty.
videos.headline: Murray rejects shot, goes southpaw on score

videos.description: Ja Morant drives the lane, then comes down with the one-handed slam over a defender.
